# NRRP Penal Code

This page lists the standard criminal, traffic, fish and game, and public order offenses used in New Republic Roleplay.

Fines and jail times are intended for roleplay balance. Officers, courts, and command staff may adjust enforcement based on the facts of the incident, officer discretion, repeat offenses, plea agreements, or court rulings.

---

# Severity Guide

| Severity | Meaning |
|---|---|
| Infraction | Citation-level offense. Usually no jail time. |
| Misdemeanor | Minor criminal offense. May include fines, short jail time, or both. |
| Felony | Serious criminal offense. Usually arrestable and may include higher jail time. |

